<div class="nopad" data-grid="container stack-3 pad-12x">
  <div data-grid="col-12">
    <h1 class="c-heading-2">Press Release &amp; Webcast</h1>
  </div>
  <div class="y-margin-bottom left" data-grid="col-9">
    <h2 class="c-subheading-2" id="erHeader">Earnings Release FY26 Q3</h2>
    <div class="row" id="pressreleasecontent">
      <div class="col-1-1">

<!-- Press Release content starts here -->

<p class="MsoNormal"><b><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:13.0pt;line-height:
115%;font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;,sans-serif;color:#666666">Microsoft Cloud and AI Strength
Fuels Third Quarter Results</span></b></p>

<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:10.0pt"><b><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;,sans-serif;
color:#666666">REDMOND, Wash. — April 29, 2026 — </span></b><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;,sans-serif;
color:#666666">Microsoft Corp. today announced the following results for the
quarter ended March 31, 2026, as compared to the corresponding period of last
fiscal year:</span></p>

<p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst" style="margin-top:6.0pt;margin-right:0in;
margin-bottom:6.0pt;margin-left:.5in;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:14.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:#666666">·<span style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;,sans-serif;
color:#666666">Revenue was $82.9 billion and increased 18% (up 15% in constant
currency)</span></p>

<p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle" style="margin-top:6.0pt;margin-right:0in;
margin-bottom:6.0pt;margin-left:.5in;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:14.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:#666666">·<span style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;,sans-serif;
color:#666666">Operating income was $38.4 billion and increased 20% (up 16% in
constant currency)</span></p>

<p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle" style="margin-top:6.0pt;margin-right:0in;
margin-bottom:6.0pt;margin-left:.5in;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:14.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:#666666">·<span style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;,sans-serif;
color:#666666">Net income was $31.8 billion and increased 23% on a GAAP basis,
and increased 20% (up 18% in constant currency) on a non-GAAP basis</span></p>

<p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle" style="margin-top:6.0pt;margin-right:0in;
margin-bottom:6.0pt;margin-left:.5in;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:14.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:#666666">·<span style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;,sans-serif;
color:#666666">Diluted earnings per share was $4.27 and increased 23% on a GAAP
basis, and increased 21% (up 18% in constant currency) on a non-GAAP basis</span></p>

<p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpLast" style="margin-top:6.0pt;margin-right:0in;
margin-bottom:6.0pt;margin-left:.5in;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:14.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:#666666">·<span style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;,sans-serif;
color:#666666">Non-GAAP results exclude the impact from investments in OpenAI, explained
in the Non-GAAP Definition section below</span></p>

<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
12.0pt;margin-left:0in"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:
115%;font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;,sans-serif;color:#666666">“We are focused on delivering cloud and AI infrastructure and solutions that empower every business to eval-max their outcomes in the agentic computing era," said Satya Nadella, chairman and chief executive officer of Microsoft. “Our AI business surpassed an annual revenue run rate of&nbsp;$37 billion, up 123% year-over-year.”</span></p>

<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
12.0pt;margin-left:0in"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:
115%;font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;,sans-serif;color:#666666">“We delivered results
that exceeded expectations across revenue, operating income, and earnings per
share, reflecting strong execution and growing demand for the Microsoft Cloud,”
said Amy Hood, executive vice president and chief financial officer of
Microsoft.</span></p>

<p style="margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:12.0pt;margin-left:
0in;line-height:115%"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:
115%;font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;,sans-serif;color:#666666">The</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;,sans-serif;
color:#666666"> following table reconciles our financial results reported in
accordance with generally accepted accounting principles (GAAP) to non-GAAP
financial results. Additional information regarding our </span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;,sans-serif;
color:#666666">non-GAAP </span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;
line-height:115%;font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;,sans-serif;color:#666666">definition is
provided below. All growth comparisons relate to the corresponding period in
