<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:0in;line-height:107%"><b><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;,sans-serif;
color:#666666">&nbsp;</span></b></p>

<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:0in;line-height:107%"><b><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;,sans-serif;
color:#666666">Business Highlights</span></b></p>

<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:10.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:
10.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;,sans-serif;color:#666666">Microsoft
Cloud revenue was $54.5 billion and increased 29% (up 25% in constant currency),
and commercial remaining performance obligation increased 99% to $627 billion.</span></p>

<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:10.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:
10.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;,sans-serif;color:#666666">Revenue
in Productivity and Business Processes was $35.0</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;,sans-serif;
color:#EE0000"> </span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:
115%;font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;,sans-serif;color:#666666">billion and increased 17%
(up 13% in constant currency), with the following business highlights:</span></p>

<p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst" style="margin-top:6.0pt;margin-right:0in;
margin-bottom:6.0pt;margin-left:.5in;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:14.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:#666666">·<span style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;,sans-serif;
color:#666666">Microsoft 365 Commercial cloud revenue increased 19% (up 15% in
constant currency)</span></p>

<p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle" style="margin-top:6.0pt;margin-right:0in;
margin-bottom:6.0pt;margin-left:.5in;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:14.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:#666666">·<span style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;,sans-serif;
color:#666666">Microsoft 365 Consumer cloud revenue increased 33% (up 29% in
constant currency) </span></p>

<p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle" style="margin-top:6.0pt;margin-right:0in;
margin-bottom:6.0pt;margin-left:.5in;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:14.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:#666666">·<span style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;,sans-serif;
color:#666666">LinkedIn revenue increased 12% (up 9% in constant currency)</span></p>

<p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpLast" style="margin-top:6.0pt;margin-right:0in;
margin-bottom:6.0pt;margin-left:.5in;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:14.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:#666666">·<span style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;,sans-serif;
color:#666666">Dynamics 365 revenue increased 22% (up 17% in constant currency)</span></p>

<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:10.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:
10.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;,sans-serif;color:#666666">Revenue
in Intelligent Cloud was $34.7 billion and increased 30% (up 28% in constant
currency), with the following business highlights:</span></p>

<p class="MsoListParagraph" style="margin-top:6.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
6.0pt;margin-left:.5in;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:14.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:#666666">·<span style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;,sans-serif;
color:#666666">Azure and other cloud services revenue increased 40% (up 39% in
constant currency)</span></p>

<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:10.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:
10.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;,sans-serif;color:#666666">Revenue
in More Personal Computing was $13.2 billion and decreased 1% (down 3% in
constant currency), with the following business highlights:</span></p>

<p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst" style="margin-top:6.0pt;margin-right:0in;
margin-bottom:6.0pt;margin-left:.5in;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:14.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:#666666">·<span style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
