<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:10.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:
10.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;,sans-serif;color:#666666">Microsoft
returned $10.2 billion to shareholders in the form of dividends and share
repurchases in the third quarter of fiscal year 2026. </span></p>

<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:16.0pt"><b><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;,sans-serif;
color:#666666">Business Outlook</span></b></p>

