</span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;,sans-serif;
color:#666666">focus on cloud-based and AI services presenting execution and
competitive risks;</span></p>

<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="margin-top:6.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
6.0pt;margin-left:.5in;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:14.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:#666666">·<span style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;,sans-serif;
color:#666666">significant investments in products and services that may not
achieve expected returns;</span></p>

<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="margin-top:6.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
6.0pt;margin-left:.5in;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:14.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:#666666">·<span style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;,sans-serif;
color:#666666">acquisitions, joint ventures, and strategic alliances that could
have an adverse effect on our business;</span></p>

<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="margin-top:6.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
6.0pt;margin-left:.5in;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:14.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:#666666">·<span style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;,sans-serif;
color:#666666">cyberattacks and security vulnerabilities that could lead to
reduced revenue, increased costs, liability claims, or harm to our reputation
or competitive position;</span></p>

<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="margin-top:6.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
6.0pt;margin-left:.5in;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:14.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:#666666">·<span style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;,sans-serif;
color:#666666">disclosure and misuse of personal data that could cause
liability and harm to our reputation; </span></p>

<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="margin-top:6.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
6.0pt;margin-left:.5in;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:14.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:#666666">·<span style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;,sans-serif;
color:#666666">the possibility that we may not be able to protect information
in our products and services from use by others;</span></p>

<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="margin-top:6.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
6.0pt;margin-left:.5in;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:14.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:#666666">·<span style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;,sans-serif;
color:#666666">abuse of our advertising, professional, marketplace, or gaming
platforms that may harm our reputation or user engagement;</span></p>

<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="margin-top:6.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
6.0pt;margin-left:.5in;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:14.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:#666666">·<span style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;,sans-serif;
color:#666666">products and services, how they are used by customers, and how
third-party products and services interact with them, presenting security,
privacy, and execution risks;</span></p>

<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="margin-top:6.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
6.0pt;margin-left:.5in;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:14.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:#666666">·<span style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;,sans-serif;
color:#666666">issues about the use of AI in our offerings that may result in
reputational or competitive harm, or liability; </span></p>

<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="margin-top:6.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
6.0pt;margin-left:.5in;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:14.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:#666666">·<span style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;,sans-serif;
color:#666666">excessive outages, data losses, and disruptions of our online
services if we fail to maintain an adequate operations infrastructure;</span></p>

<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="margin-top:6.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
6.0pt;margin-left:.5in;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:14.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:#666666">·<span style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;,sans-serif;
color:#666666">supply or quality problems;</span></p>

<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="margin-top:6.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
6.0pt;margin-left:.5in;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:14.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:#666666">·<span style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;,sans-serif;
color:#666666">potential consequences of new, existing, and evolving legal and
regulatory requirements;</span></p>

<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="margin-top:6.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
6.0pt;margin-left:.5in;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:14.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:#666666">·<span style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;,sans-serif;
color:#666666">claims against us that could result in adverse outcomes in legal
disputes;</span></p>

<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="margin-top:6.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
6.0pt;margin-left:.5in;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:14.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:#666666">·<span style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;,sans-serif;
color:#666666">uncertainties relating to our business with government
customers;</span></p>

<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="margin-top:6.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
6.0pt;margin-left:.5in;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:14.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:#666666">·<span style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;,sans-serif;
color:#666666">additional tax liabilities;</span></p>

<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="margin-top:6.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
6.0pt;margin-left:.5in;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:14.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:#666666">·<span style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;,sans-serif;
color:#666666">an inability to protect and utilize our intellectual property
may harm our business and operating results;</span></p>

<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="margin-top:6.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
6.0pt;margin-left:.5in;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:14.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:#666666">·<span style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;,sans-serif;
color:#666666">claims that Microsoft has infringed the intellectual property
rights of others;</span></p>

<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="margin-top:6.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
6.0pt;margin-left:.5in;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:14.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:#666666">·<span style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;,sans-serif;
color:#666666">damage to our reputation or our brands that may harm our
business and results of operations;</span></p>

<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="margin-top:6.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
6.0pt;margin-left:.5in;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:14.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:#666666">·<span style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;,sans-serif;
color:#666666">adverse economic or market conditions that could harm our
business; </span></p>

<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="margin-top:6.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
6.0pt;margin-left:.5in;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:14.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:#666666">·<span style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;,sans-serif;
color:#666666">catastrophic events or geopolitical conditions, such as the
COVID-19 pandemic, that could disrupt our business; </span></p>

<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="margin-top:6.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
6.0pt;margin-left:.5in;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:14.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:#666666">·<span style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;,sans-serif;
color:#666666">exposure to increased economic and operational uncertainties
from operating a global business, including the effects of foreign currency
exchange; and</span></p>

<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="margin-top:6.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
6.0pt;margin-left:.5in;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:14.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:#666666">·<span style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;,sans-serif;
color:#666666">the dependence of our business on our ability to attract and
retain talented employees.</span></p>

<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
10.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:115%"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:
10.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;,sans-serif;color:#666666">For
more information about risks and uncertainties associated with Microsoft’s
business, please refer to the “Management’s Discussion and Analysis of
